Hey Courtney,
Make sure that your dizzy is clean and your advance mechanisms (vacuum 
and spring) are both functioning correctly.  I had a dirty advance plate 
that was causing my idle to stay high.  Have you rebuilt your entire 
dizzy lately?  It can do wonders...

Mike

